<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Autoshop.ba</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
        }

        .navbar {
            background-color: #007bff; 
        }

        .navbar-brand {
            font-size: 1.8rem;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: white !important;
        }

        .navbar-nav {
            margin-left: auto;
        }

        .hero-section {
            background-color: #007bff; 
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 120px 20px;
        }

        .hero-section h1 {
            font-size: 3rem;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .hero-section p {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

        .btn-primary {
            background-color: white;
            color: #007bff;
            border: none;
            padding: 12px 25px;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }

        .btn-primary:hover {
            background-color: #007bff;
            color: white;
        }

        .admin-home {
            padding: 60px 20px;
            background-color: #007bff; 
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
            border-radius: 10px;
            margin: 40px auto;
            max-width: 80%;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        .admin-home h1 {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
        }

        .admin-home p {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
        }

        .features-section {
            padding: 60px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .feature-card {
            background: white;
            border: 2px solid #007bff;
            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .feature-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
            box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
        }

        .feature-icon {
            font-size: 3rem;
            color: #007bff;
        }

        .footer {
            background-color: #007bff;
            color: white;
            padding: 20px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg navbar-dark">
        <div class="container">
            <a class="navbar-brand" href="#">Autoshop.ba</a>
            <button class="navbar-toggler" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#navbarNav">
                <span class="navbar-toggler-icon"></span>
            </button>
            <div class="collapse navbar-collapse" id="navbarNav">
                <ul class="navbar-nav ms-auto">
                    
                    <li class="nav-item">
                        <a class="btn btn-outline-light" href="/autoshop.ba/logout">Logout</a>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </nav>


    <div class="hero-section">
        <div class="container">
            <h1>Welcome, <%= username %> !</h1> 
            <p>Manage your car ads, offers, and user interactions with ease. Post, update, and delete ads, respond to inquiries, and much more—all in one place!</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="container features-section">
        <div class="row text-center">
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <div class="feature-card shadow-sm rounded">
                    <i class="feature-icon bi bi-person-circle"></i>
                    <h3 class="mt-3">My Ads</h3>
                    <p>Keep track of all your car listings and easily manage your posted ads. <br></p>
                    <a href="/seller/myads" class="btn btn-primary">Manage Ads</a>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <div class="feature-card shadow-sm rounded">
                    <i class="feature-icon bi bi-file-earmark-post"></i>
                    <h3 class="mt-3">Create ad</h3>
                    <p>Looking to sell your car? Start by creating a detailed ad to attract potential buyers.</p>
                    <a href="/seller/create/ad" class="btn btn-primary">Create ad</a>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <div class="feature-card shadow-sm rounded">
                    <i class="feature-icon bi bi-bar-chart-line"></i>
                    <h3 class="mt-3">Manage Offers</h3>
                    <p>Review all the offers for your car and make decisions. Your car, your choice!</p>
                    <a href="/seller/bids" class="btn btn-primary">View Offers</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <footer class="footer">
        <div class="container">
            <p class="mb-0">&copy; 2025 Autoshop.ba | Developed by Emir Babačić</p>
        </div>
    </footer>

</body>
</html>